Paul Orude, Bauchi Bauchi State Deputy Governor Engineer Nuhu has resigned. Daily Sun gathered that Gidado’s resignation was contained in a letter addressed to Governor Mohammed Abubakar dated May 16, 2018. The erstwhile deputy governor who was rarely seen in public of recent said he pledged to be in office for a single term but was forced to resign before the expiration of the first tenure owing to what he termed ” waning political atmosphere. He thanked the governor whom he called “my brother” for the opportunity to serve the people of the state…….details later